Modules and their roles :

*.h - header files that contains function declarations and macro definitions to be shared between the source files.
fetch.cpp - fetches details requested in main.cpp.
distro_art.cpp - contains the ASCII art for all distros that dafetch supports.
main.cpp - with the help of the files mentioned above,puts every detail together to output what you see when you run dafetch.


